(Earl's Wife, Su Ke's Tablet)

13
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:45,230
Now,

14
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:48,390
the three of you swear

15
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,640
on your mother's tablet

16
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,840
that you'll never

17
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:55,280
avenge her death

18
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:58,640
on the Grand Princess.

19
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,790
Do you hear me?

20
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,120
No.

21
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:07,430
Si has confirmed

22
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,400
that she had Xiao

23
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,510
kill our mother.

24
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,440
As her son,

25
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,390
I must avenge her death.

26
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,750
- You fool!
- Zhan!

27
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,440
Who do you think you are?

28
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:23,080
What can you do to her?

29
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,480
Father,

30
00:02:28,150 --> 00:02:29,760
I know you mean to protect us.

31
00:02:30,710 --> 00:02:32,440
The Grand Princess is too powerful.

32
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:35,440
You fear

33
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,710
we'll fail and end up dead,

34
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,040
right?

35
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,160
Yi,

36
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,790
you're the eldest.

37
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,200
You're also a parent.

38
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,000
You know better than anyone

39
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,200
how I feel as your father.

40
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,200
Right now,

41
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:56,400
if your daughter, Yan,

42
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,510
were in danger,

43
00:02:57,750 --> 00:03:00,150
wouldn't you protect her

44
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,760
at all costs?

45
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:03,830
I don't want anything

46
00:03:04,470 --> 00:03:06,430
but the three of you

47
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:09,880
living in peace for the rest of your lives.

48
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:11,520
Back then,

49
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:13,320
I failed to protect your mother.

50
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,720
Now,

51
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:18,590
whatever it takes,

52
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:21,440
I can't put you in harm's way!

53
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,950
Swear to me now.

54
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,280
Fine.

55
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,160
I swear to you.

56
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,600
Yi!

57
00:03:34,470 --> 00:03:35,390
You've

58
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,950
always been the most obedient.

59
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,320
I never need to worry about you.

60
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:42,550
Father!

61
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:43,670
If you

62
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:45,240
insist on

63
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,270
risking your life for revenge,

64
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:50,320
then get out of this house.

65
00:03:50,710 --> 00:03:51,630
And your name

66
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,390
will be removed from our pedigree.

67
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,640
I, Jiang Ancheng...

68
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:01,710
I, Jiang Ancheng,

69
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:04,790
will no longer see you as my son.

70
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,920
Father!

71
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:08,480
If you still think I'm your father,

72
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,830
swear to me right now.

73
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,280
Fine.

74
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,710
I won't take revenge

75
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:30,950
or stir up trouble.

76
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:34,510
Happy now?

77
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,830
Are you happy now?

78
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,040
Si,

79
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,640
Zhan and Yi have sworn to me.

80
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,600
Will you?

81
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,160
Father,

82
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:11,190
do you really think we'll be safe

83
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,470
by letting go of the past?

84
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:15,000
My mother compromised over and over,

85
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,870
suffering in silence,

86
00:05:15,870 --> 00:05:17,950
but did the Grand Princess spare her?

87
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,310
Now that we know who killed her,

88
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:21,600
why can't we take revenge?

89
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,600
How can we let the killer

90
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,800
get away and enjoy her life?

91
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,470
I won't swear to you

92
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,350
no matter what.

93
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,920
Whether you'll remove my name

94
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,150
from our pedigree

95
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,120
or kick me out of our house,

96
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,830
I swear revenge on the killer.

97
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,000
The Grand Princess must pay

98
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,920
with blood!

99
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,270
Shut up!

100
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:40,870
Si!

101
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:43,680
- Father...
- You're too young.

102
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,120
You have no idea

103
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,910
about the Grand Princess's might.

104
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:52,310
She's favored by His Majesty

105
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,560
who's the only one above her.

106
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:57,270
There's no way we can bring her down.

107
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,800
Little strokes fell great oaks!

108
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,920
We haven't even tried.

109
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,270
How do you know we can't?

110
00:06:01,270 --> 00:06:02,270
What will you do?

111
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,800
What can you do?

112
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:07,560
File a suit to His Majesty?

113
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,830
Before you can beat the drum

114
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,000
outside the court,

115
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,270
she's cooked up

116
00:06:13,270 --> 00:06:14,360
tons of charges against you

117
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,830
without lifting a finger.

118
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:18,760
Or will you poison her as well

119
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,080
or assassinate her?

120
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:23,480
You know you're weak and delicate.

121
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:26,150
Will you succeed?

122
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:27,880
Si,

123
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,120
how else should I put it

124
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:32,320
to make you give up?

125
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:36,030
Father...

126
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:39,510
Father...

127
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,560
I've...

128
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,800
I've lost your mother.

129
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:48,240
I cannot lose you either.

130
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:55,200
I can't!

131
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,920
Father.

132
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,440
Come here, Jin.

133
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,760
Let's see who will win.

134
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:27,190
Sure.

135
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,310
Jin,

136
00:07:40,630 --> 00:07:42,270
Supervisor Yang of Astronomy

137
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:44,590
handed in a report yesterday.

138
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:45,750
He asserted

139
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,560
that if you married a girl

140
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,830
who was born a jinx,

141
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,920
it'd harm

142
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:53,080
our family and state.

143
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,800
Dazhou would be in chaos.

144
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,960
Do you believe that?

145
00:08:02,190 --> 00:08:03,640
All the officials do.

146
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:06,350
Water can carry a boat but also overturn it.

147
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,760
Although an emperor is above everyone,

148
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:12,240
he can't shut all of them up.

149
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,280
Jin,

150
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:15,440
if disasters happen,

151
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,560
I don't want others

152
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,950
to pin everything on you again.

153
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:21,030
The one who was "born a jinx"

154
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,510
as Supervisor Yang said

155
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,350
was Jiang Si, right?

156
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,070
Yes.

157
00:08:26,070 --> 00:08:27,710
You've issued the edict of betrothal.

158
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,800
You can't take that back.

159
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:32,470
By Supervisor Yang's calculation,

160
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:34,080
Cui Mingyue's date of birth

161
00:08:34,630 --> 00:08:36,160
complements Jiang Si's.

162
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:38,400
If you marry them both,

163
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:42,160
it'll neutralize the harm.

164
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,440
I've asked the Grand Princess.

165
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:46,870
She'll marry Mingyue to you

166
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:49,470
for the greater good.

167
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,990
But I won't marry her.

168
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,920
Mingyue is a Commandery Princess.

169
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,280
In terms of status,

170
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:58,520
she's a better match than Jiang Si.

171
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:01,560
Father, I've made my decision.

172
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,230
Why bring trouble on myself?

173
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,280
Jiang Si is what my heart yearns for

174
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:09,830
and belongs to.

175
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:15,670
Go home and think it over.

176
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,750
Then tell me your decision.

177
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:18,000
I don't need more time to think.

178
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,160
This is my decision.

179
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,320
Father, if there's nothing else,

180
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:25,830
I shall take my leave.

181
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,630
If I allowed

182
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,630
other princes

183
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,040
to marry two girls together,

184
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:44,080
they couldn't thank me enough for that.

185
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,470
What a stubborn mule.

186
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:58,320
I know I'm guilty.

187
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,870
I've knelt for a day and a night

188
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:05,080
without eating anything.

189
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:07,110
Your Highness,

190
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:10,440
please spare me.

191
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,400
When you were little,

192
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,160
you'd cry in your sleep.

193
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:22,590
I had to hold you

194
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,200
every night to comfort you.

195
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,350
Before you turned three,

196
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:30,110
I hadn't had one good night's sleep.

197
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:33,320
That's why I tended to

198
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:34,870
sleep a lot afterward.

199
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:38,320
I'm too old.

200
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,960
They beat gongs and drums

201
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,400
to keep me from dozing off.

202
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:45,230
I couldn't take it anymore

203
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,990
and let it slip!

204
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,920
How have I treated you these years?

205
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,350
However many people in this house

206
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,400
told me you overreached yourself,

207
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:02,920
I ignored them and tolerated you.

208
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:06,270
How dare you betray me!

209
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:07,630
Spare me, Your Highness!

210
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,910
I only said

211
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:10,910
Su Ke

212
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:13,320
was flirtatious and seductive

213
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,470
in front of men.

214
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:15,830
Being poisoned

215
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:17,400
to death

216
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:18,790
was her karma.

217
00:11:18,790 --> 00:11:19,970
Did you tell them about Nanwu?

218
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,070
I wouldn't dare

219
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:25,390
say a word about it.

220
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:27,400
Your Highness, I have news for you.

221
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:28,950
Come in.

222
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,120
Your Highness,

223
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,560
Prince Yan refused His Majesty's offer.

224
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:35,590
He wouldn't marry Princess Mingyue.

225
00:11:40,030 --> 00:11:42,270
(Graceful and Dignified)
I admire loyal couples the most.

226
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,320
They won't have their way.

227
00:11:46,630 --> 00:11:47,800
If Jiang Si

228
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:49,390
refuses to die of poison

229
00:11:49,390 --> 00:11:50,990
like Su Ke,

230
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:54,200
we'll do something else.

231
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,750
Yes, Your Highness.

232
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,910
After leaving the Palace yesterday,

233
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,990
Prince Yan went to find

234
00:11:58,990 --> 00:12:00,270
those two officials of Astronomy.

235
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:02,030
Luckily, we had silenced those two

236
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,280
beforehand.

237
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:05,110
That was wise of you.

238
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,870
Did you leak it?

239
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:12,880
Otherwise,

240
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:15,440
he wouldn't have gone to check overnight.

241
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,630
I accidentally

242
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,120
told his guard

243
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,750
about 20 years ago.

244
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:21,750
That was all my fault!

245
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:22,830
Useless!

246
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:26,750
I'm sorry, Your Highness!

247
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:28,950
I deserve death!

248
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,350
Wait... Your Highness,

249
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:36,400
the dead can't talk.

250
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:38,440
What I said

251
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,990
is also vague.

252
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,110
Prince Yan can't find any evidence.

253
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:45,510
He won't report you

254
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:46,710
to His Majesty.

255
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:48,590
I dare him!

256
00:12:49,870 --> 00:12:51,440
Brother has so many children.

257
00:12:52,270 --> 00:12:54,120
He didn't even grow up in the Palace.

258
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,320
He's a nobody.

259
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:57,080
How dare he report me!

260
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,080
The dead can't talk.

261
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:04,920
Actually, you remind me of that.

262
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:06,790
Servant.

263
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:14,670
What now?

264
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,830
You refuse to drink

265
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,280
the tea from me?

266
00:13:32,910 --> 00:13:34,080
Your Highness,

267
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,920
your arm was once injured.

268
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:40,440
Other servants can be clumsy.

269
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:45,200
If you aren't used to their service,

270
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:48,080
and you'd rather have me instead,

271
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:51,630
my life is worth it.

272
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,080
What are you talking about?

273
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:14,110
You breastfed me.

274
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:16,950
I'll give you another chance, of course.

275
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:20,120
Yesterday, if you believed

276
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,670
I'd kill you for sure

277
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:23,280
and didn't come back with me,

278
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,280
you'd become

279
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:29,870
one of the dead who couldn't talk.

280
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:35,800
The tea is a reward and punishment.

281
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,830
Next time,

282
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,350
however soft I am,

283
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:41,920
I will not spare you.

284
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:44,830
Thanks for your mercy, Your Highness!

285
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,970
When I was alone in the room with Ms. Xu,

286
00:14:47,970 --> 00:14:48,450
she let slip

287
00:14:48,450 --> 00:14:49,520
that the Grand Princess had

288
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:50,720
tried to ruin you 20 years ago.

289
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:51,640
20 years ago?

290
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,150
When I was called cursed

291
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:55,400
by the Directorate of Astronomy?

292
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,990
Was that her doing?

293
00:14:57,310 --> 00:14:58,200
By the way, Chief,

294
00:14:58,200 --> 00:14:59,190
Mr. Xiao's letter arrived

