00:14:59,190 --> 00:15:00,440
from Lingshui earlier today.

296
00:15:05,870 --> 00:15:08,920
"Observer Jiang Ancheng also knows."

297
00:15:11,540 --> 00:15:14,020
(Jiang)

298
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:29,920
(Father,)

299
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,120
(do you really think we'll be safe)

300
00:15:33,120 --> 00:15:34,200
(by letting go of the past?)

301
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:36,750
(My mother compromised over and over,)

302
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:37,670
(suffering in silence,)

303
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,680
(but did the Grand Princess spare her?)

304
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,360
(Now that we know who killed her,)

305
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,590
(why can't we take revenge?)

306
00:15:45,790 --> 00:15:46,840
(How can we let the killer)

307
00:15:46,840 --> 00:15:47,990
(get away and enjoy her life?)

308
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,440
- Your Highness.
- Sir.

309
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:04,080
Why did you ask to see me

310
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,240
this late, sir?

311
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,920
Please have a seat.

312
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,280
Do you know

313
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:18,520
I disapprove of Si

314
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,110
marrying you?

315
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:21,310
I do.

316
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,520
I hoped that she'd

317
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:26,040
lead a peaceful life.

318
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,280
Even if

319
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:30,280
it'd be ordinary,

320
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:31,230
I didn't want her...

321
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:33,240
I know you don't want her to be involved

322
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,520
in power struggle.

323
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:36,190
Neither do I.

324
00:16:39,150 --> 00:16:40,590
There is something

325
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:43,470
I've kept to myself for years.

326
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,800
No one else knows.

327
00:16:46,270 --> 00:16:47,350
I'm afraid

328
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:51,280
it greatly concerns you.

329
00:16:51,550 --> 00:16:53,120
20 years ago,

330
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:55,720
I was an official in Astronomy.

331
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:56,640
I know that.

332
00:16:58,200 --> 00:16:59,440
I've talked to Mr. Chu

333
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,360
and Mr. Xiao.

334
00:17:00,790 --> 00:17:01,710
I was wondering

335
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:03,680
how I should bring that up,

336
00:17:03,910 --> 00:17:05,110
and here you are

337
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,080
being candid about it.

338
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:09,280
Alright then.

339
00:17:09,510 --> 00:17:11,080
I'll cut to the chase.

340
00:17:14,110 --> 00:17:17,280
You weren't born cursed.

341
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,910
On the contrary,

342
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:21,350
that night,

343
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:23,110
when I observed the sky,

344
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:25,520
it showed a great omen!

345
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:29,910
In the 3rd year of Jingming,

346
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:32,110
on the 5th day of the 5th month...

347
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:37,670
Mr. Jiang,

348
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:40,150
(Astronomy)
the sky seems abnormal tonight.

349
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:43,280
Supervisor Yang sent us to take your shift.

350
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,430
You may come down.

351
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,680
Gentlemen,

352
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,590
(Astronomy)
here's my observation tonight.

353
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:50,150
I think it's a great omen!

354
00:17:50,790 --> 00:17:52,480
It's not the time yet.

355
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:54,270
You've stayed up all night.

356
00:17:54,270 --> 00:17:55,590
Go back and rest.

357
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:56,510
Sure.

358
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,670
I'll take my leave then.

359
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,640
Mr. Xiao,

360
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,720
why would the Grand Princess brand

361
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:04,550
a newborn prince a cursed boy?

362
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:05,540
(In the 3rd...)
You know

363
00:18:05,540 --> 00:18:07,240
(North Star...)
what happened in the South?

364
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,800
Nanwu invaded our border.

365
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,590
(...a great omen.)
Our garrison suffered

366
00:18:10,590 --> 00:18:11,830
the worst defeat ever.

367
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:15,750
But what was that to do

368
00:18:15,750 --> 00:18:16,830
with that prince?

369
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,960
Their commander is Cui Xu.

370
00:18:20,350 --> 00:18:22,000
The Grand Princess's husband?

371
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,310
The prince's mother, Consort Xian,

372
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:25,000
will soon become a Noble Consort.

373
00:18:25,310 --> 00:18:26,790
The Grand Princess

374
00:18:26,790 --> 00:18:28,080
cannot allow it.

375
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,560
A cursed prince will be

376
00:18:29,570 --> 00:18:31,440
a heavy blow to Consort Xian

377
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:32,720
and help Cui Xu out,

378
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,670
killing two birds with one stone.

379
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,640
I can't believe that in order to

380
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:41,280
prevent Cui Xu from being punished

381
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,720
and my mother from being promoted,

382
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:45,110
the Grand Princess

383
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:46,910
reversed my fate!

384
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:51,040
I feel guilty about it.

385
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,110
Back then,

386
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:55,760
I was too afraid of the Grand Princess

387
00:18:56,030 --> 00:18:57,440
to bring her scheme to light

388
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,920
or tell the truth

389
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,520
to uphold justice.

390
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:02,480
Now, I'm cornered.

391
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:05,760
They've killed my wife.

392
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:07,960
Si is their next target.

393
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:08,880
Sir,

394
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,480
she doesn't want you to get involved

395
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,590
in this mess either.

396
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:14,960
I'll find the evidence

397
00:19:15,510 --> 00:19:16,590
against the culprit myself.

398
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:17,800
Your Highness,

399
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:20,040
the Annal of Divination
for the year you were born

400
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,670
can be the evidence.

401
00:19:22,550 --> 00:19:26,320
As much as I feared to be in trouble,

402
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:27,520
I didn't want the truth

403
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,830
to be buried forever.

404
00:19:32,030 --> 00:19:33,430
(That explains why Father)

405
00:19:33,790 --> 00:19:34,720
(tried to stop me)

406
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:35,830
(from marrying Yu Qi.)

407
00:19:37,620 --> 00:19:44,620
(Majesty and Prestige)

408
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:47,000
The Grand Princess planted

409
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,190
spies into the harem.

410
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,520
She must've been prepared.

411
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:51,110
Your safety comes first.

412
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:53,670
Be careful when you gather information.

413
00:19:54,030 --> 00:19:54,950
You too.

414
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,330
The Directorate of Astronomy

415
00:19:56,330 --> 00:19:57,480
is tough to deal with.

416
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,510
What the divination was

417
00:19:58,510 --> 00:19:59,430
when you were born

418
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:01,080
will be found out eventually.

419
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,630
Don't act rashly

420
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,400
or risk your life.

421
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:07,840
I know.

422
00:20:07,840 --> 00:20:10,620
(Tiande Hall)

423
00:20:10,830 --> 00:20:11,830
Ever since His Majesty

424
00:20:11,830 --> 00:20:13,480
issued the edict of betrothal,

425
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:15,590
Jin has become a laughingstock

426
00:20:15,590 --> 00:20:17,150
in the entire harem.

427
00:20:17,510 --> 00:20:18,830
They say he's uncultured

428
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,440
as he grew up in the South.

429
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,480
He's ignorant,

430
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,320
short-sighted, and simple-minded.

431
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:25,670
I'm furious!

432
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,080
Please calm down.

433
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:33,560
Mother, I'm not sure

434
00:20:34,270 --> 00:20:35,560
if I should say this.

435
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:36,640
Out with it.

436
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:38,110
Don't be bashful.

437
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:40,440
Miss Jiang Si is

438
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,870
really something else.

439
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:44,760
She outshone all the girls,

440
00:20:45,110 --> 00:20:47,000
including Princess Mingyue, at the banquet.

441
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,030
Even Father was

442
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:50,390
impressed by her.

443
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:53,350
To think if she disobeys you

444
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:57,040
while Prince Yan takes her side...

445
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:00,280
How is she my match?

446
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:03,040
You, go to Earl Dongping's Mansion.

447
00:21:03,350 --> 00:21:05,000
Summon her to the Jinhua Hall

448
00:21:05,510 --> 00:21:06,720
to be lectured.

449
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:07,990
Yes.

450
00:21:09,830 --> 00:21:10,750
Your Highness,

451
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:13,320
Miss Si is right outside

452
00:21:13,590 --> 00:21:14,960
to pay her respects to you.

453
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:18,870
Perfect timing.

454
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,080
Send her in.

455
00:21:20,310 --> 00:21:21,200
Yes.

456
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,270
I'm here as the Commandant

457
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,800
of Capital Security

458
00:21:23,920 --> 00:21:25,000
to check

459
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,350
certain files in your archives.

460
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,960
Please be cooperative, Mr. Yang.

461
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:29,920
(Astronomy)
Prince Yan,

462
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,720
all our archives have been

463
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:34,000
stored in the warehouse.

464
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:35,870
To access them,

465
00:21:36,550 --> 00:21:37,470
you'll need

466
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:39,030
a reading permit

467
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:40,240
with His Majesty's seal.

468
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:41,880
Of course.

469
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:50,720
As far as I remember,

470
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:52,030
this reading permit

471
00:21:52,030 --> 00:21:52,950
was granted

472
00:21:53,180 --> 00:21:54,030
when you and Mr. Zhen

473
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:55,630
investigated the Hunt Case, right?

474
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:57,130
There are unanswered questions,

475
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:59,030
requiring further investigation. Problem?

476
00:21:59,030 --> 00:22:00,320
His Majesty is fair and just.

477
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:01,750
The Directorate

478
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:03,590
has dismissed those involved in that case.

479
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:04,960
What else

480
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:06,560
needs to be investigated?

481
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:09,440
- Has the permit expired?
- Not yet.

482
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:10,790
- Has the case closed?
- Not yet.

483
00:22:10,790 --> 00:22:12,510
Your persistent hindrance makes you

484
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:13,550
look guilty, Mr. Yang.

485
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:14,590
Looks like

486
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,430
I have to report everything to His Majesty.

487
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,990
- Please.
- Thanks.

488
00:22:23,020 --> 00:22:24,620
(Astronomy)
Uh, Chief.

489
00:22:24,920 --> 00:22:26,510
My stomach hurts all of a sudden.

490
00:22:26,510 --> 00:22:27,430
Show him, Mr. Yang.

491
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,600
Go straight.

492
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:30,640
Thanks, Mr. Yang.

493
00:22:33,510 --> 00:22:35,080
Jiang Si of Earl Dongping's Mansion

494
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:36,910
greets you, Your Highness.

495
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:39,280
May you live long and prosper.

496
00:22:39,960 --> 00:22:40,920
Miss Si,

497
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:42,670
when paying your respects for the first time,

498
00:22:42,960 --> 00:22:45,100
(Ms. Lin)
you should also kowtow.

499
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:47,800
Didn't your family teach you that?

500
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,080
My apologies.

501
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:02,390
I greet you, Your Highness.

502
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:04,590
May you live long and prosper.

503
00:23:15,920 --> 00:23:17,190
Your manner

504
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,520
doesn't look too bad.

505
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,590
Thanks, Your Highness.

506
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:30,110
Her Highness hasn't allowed you up.

507
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:32,910
Listen to her lecture on your knees.

508
00:23:44,030 --> 00:23:44,950
Yes.

509
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:47,760
I heard

510
00:23:48,110 --> 00:23:49,830
your mother was from a house of merchants.

511
00:23:50,510 --> 00:23:53,960
As humble as Earl Dongping's Mansion is,

512
00:23:54,310 --> 00:23:56,150
your ancestors were noble

513
00:23:56,790 --> 00:23:58,520
with ranks.

514
00:23:59,030 --> 00:24:00,910
How did they let your mother in?

515
00:24:01,350 --> 00:24:02,280
Or

516
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:05,110
did you learn from her

517
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:07,150
about how to marry up?

518
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:11,520
Your Highness,

519
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:13,520
I lost my mother

520
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,080
when I was born.

521
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:17,110
Although I was unable to

522
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:19,190
grow up with her,

523
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:21,720
I heard a lot from others

524
00:24:22,030 --> 00:24:23,760
about her virtue

525
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,280
and integrity.

526
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:27,110
She's my role model.

527
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:29,320
Compared with those who lived

528
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:30,720
but abandoned their children

529
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:32,560
and taught them nothing,

530
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,240
my mother is much better.

531
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:35,280
How dare you

532
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,350
make such insinuating remarks against me!

533
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:40,280
Slap her!

534
00:24:47,830 --> 00:24:49,190
Are the rest of you dead? Go!

535
00:24:52,110 --> 00:24:53,030
Let me go!

536
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:56,480
Mother,

537
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:58,140
this is only her first visit to the Palace.

538
00:24:58,270 --> 00:24:59,480
Please show mercy

539
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:00,760
and spare her this time.

540
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:02,390
If she gets hurt,

541
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:04,670
Prince Jin will be worried and mad.

542
00:25:05,310 --> 00:25:07,670
It might ruin the bond between you two.

543
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,520
Slap her!

544
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:31,000
If I hadn't vented my anger,

545
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:33,240
I probably wouldn't have made it

546
00:25:33,240 --> 00:25:34,830
to the day we bonded.

547
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:36,640
Ms. Lin.

548
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:37,920
Yes.

549
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:38,870
First, Jiang Si was

550
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:41,520
betrothed to Duke An's heir.

551
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:43,760
Then she and the Zhen Clan were close.

552
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:45,920
You

553
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,520
shall check her

554
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:51,240
thoroughly for me

555
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:52,550
to see

556
00:25:52,550 --> 00:25:55,350
if she's still a virgin.

557
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:56,750
Your Highness,

558
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:58,000
you can't insult me like that!

559
00:25:58,270 --> 00:25:59,190
Princess Qi!

560
00:26:00,310 --> 00:26:01,230
Let go of me!

561
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:09,760
Don't be mad, Mother.

562
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:14,190
Her mother had died years ago.

563
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:15,520
Why didn't you tell me that?

564
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:20,000
Did you mean to give her a chance

565
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:21,480
to mock me?

566
00:26:22,880 --> 00:26:25,430
I apologize for my negligence.

567
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:27,320
Let go of me!

568
00:26:27,770 --> 00:26:28,630
Let go...!

569
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,350
Gag her already!

570
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:33,230
Don't touch me,

571
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,280
or Prince Yan will make you pay!

572
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:39,510
Have you lost your virginity?

573
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,670
Are you afraid we'll find out,

574
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:42,990
so you're threatening us with your life?

575
00:26:44,750 --> 00:26:46,430
- Seize her!
- Step back!

576
00:26:47,030 --> 00:26:47,950
Tell them to leave.

577
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:52,880
Do as I say!

578
00:26:54,310 --> 00:26:55,230
Get out!

579
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:00,040
Ms. Lin, before you check me,

580
00:27:01,680 --> 00:27:03,190
feel that cut in your palm.

581
00:27:04,110 --> 00:27:05,150
It hurts badly, huh?

582
00:27:05,750 --> 00:27:06,670
Is it

583
00:27:07,400 --> 00:27:08,910
also getting itchy?

584
00:27:11,440 --> 00:27:12,430
What did you do to me?

585
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:16,320
You must've heard

586
00:27:17,110 --> 00:27:18,320
that at the banquet,

587
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:20,350
I had recognized the Traceless Grass

588
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:23,190
and made flowers bloom instantly.

589
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,100
If I could've done all that,

590
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:27,320
I could've certainly

591
00:27:30,010 --> 00:27:31,150
smeared poison on this shard.

592
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,510
You're bluffing.

593
00:27:36,510 --> 00:27:37,430
Am I?

594
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:39,080
Believe it or not,

595
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,630
if you don't take the antidote

596
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,960
before the sunset,

597
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:45,800
tonight, you'll bleed

598
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:48,240
from the seven holes in your head and die.

599
00:27:49,030 --> 00:27:50,280
You'll die

600
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:51,960
a horrible death.

601
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,400
Miss Si,

602
00:28:02,960 --> 00:28:04,310
even if I'm coerced

603
00:28:04,310 --> 00:28:05,390
into covering for you today,

604
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:08,150
Prince Yan will find out
on your wedding night.

605
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:11,430
My virginity won't be your concern.

606
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,110
Alright, fine.

607
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:16,510
I know what to say to Her Highness.

608
00:28:17,790 --> 00:28:19,080
Give me the antidote now.

609
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,360
Miss Si!

610
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,800
That can wait.

611
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:23,710
Ms. Lin,

612
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:25,840
you've been in the Palace for decades.

613
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,760
I'd like to ask you something.

614
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,400
Ask away.

615
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:32,930
I'll tell you everything I know.

616
00:28:33,550 --> 00:28:34,760
Which lady is

617
00:28:35,550 --> 00:28:37,270
Grand Princess Rongyang the closest to

618
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:38,390
in the harem?

619
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:39,560
Consort Zhuang

620
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:41,350
and Empress Di.

621
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:42,670
Empress Di?

622
00:28:43,320 --> 00:28:44,160
That's right.

623
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,560
After Empress Qingrong passed away,

624
00:28:46,430 --> 00:28:47,310
the Grand Princess

625
00:28:47,310 --> 00:28:48,970
nominated her first to be the next empress.

626
00:28:52,550 --> 00:28:54,280
Do Consort Zhuang and Empress Di

627
00:28:54,590 --> 00:28:55,440
have senior maids

628
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:56,860
who have served for almost 20 years?

629
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:59,350
I don't know exactly

630
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:00,960
how long their maids have served,

631
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:04,560
but the ones by their sides

632
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:06,240
are senior to the others.

633
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:09,190
Why do you ask?

634
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:11,320
Please give me the antidote!

635
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:13,270
Please, Miss!

636
00:29:13,270 --> 00:29:14,110
Be patient.

637
00:29:14,110 --> 00:29:15,560
Once I get out of the Jinhua Hall,

638
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:16,720
you'll have it.

639
00:29:17,060 --> 00:29:20,020
(Prince Yan's Mansion)

640
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:30,990
Mother!

641
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,360
Qian.

642
00:29:32,790 --> 00:29:34,320
- Mother!
- Qian!

643
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:36,600
Qian,

644
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:37,870
I thought

645
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,630
I'd never see you again.

646
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:41,040
You look much thinner

647
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:42,600
and haggard, too.

648
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:46,430
Qian,

649
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:48,520
how did you know I was here?

650
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:56,190
Mother,

651
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:57,800
what were you thinking?

652
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:00,040
Why did you poison them?

653
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,960
I wanted revenge.

654
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,150
Back then, Su Ke was

655
00:30:05,350 --> 00:30:06,590
always better than me.

656
00:30:07,590 --> 00:30:10,240
Your grandmother incited me

657
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:11,350
to compete against her.

658
00:30:11,830 --> 00:30:13,110
I had no choice.

659
00:30:13,830 --> 00:30:15,830
A while ago,

660
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,240
Prince Yan chose Jiang Si.

661
00:30:18,720 --> 00:30:20,240
She'd become Princess Yan.

662
00:30:20,790 --> 00:30:22,520
Once they got married,

663
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,590
our branch

664
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,240
would be doomed.

665
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:28,320
That's why I...

666
00:30:32,510 --> 00:30:33,800
That was terrible.

667
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:36,110
We could've

668
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:37,480
led a peaceful life in the mansion.

669
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,400
Wouldn't that be nice?

670
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:40,450
Why did you do things that hurt yourself

671
00:30:41,450 --> 00:30:42,350
and others?

672
00:30:42,350 --> 00:30:43,560
Well, back then...

673
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,030
Back then?

674
00:30:46,030 --> 00:30:47,350
What happened?

675
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:50,160
Never mind.

676
00:30:51,750 --> 00:30:53,240
It was a long time ago.

677
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,400
No need to rake it up.

678
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:57,630
I've reflected on myself.

679
00:30:58,640 --> 00:31:00,390
Given all those mistakes I made,

680
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,760
I owe the First Branch too much.

681
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:05,720
I have to pay off my debts.

682
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:07,520
Please talk to your father

683
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,760
to let me go back.

684
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:12,150
I'll be their slave to...

685
00:31:12,590 --> 00:31:13,510
Mother,

686
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:17,280
I'm afraid you can't go back.

687
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:20,160
Perhaps Father is thinking about

688
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:21,520
making Ms. Ruan his wife.

689
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,190
After what happened,

690
00:31:24,750 --> 00:31:25,830
you're dead to him

691
00:31:27,310 --> 00:31:28,960
even if you're still alive.

692
00:31:32,240 --> 00:31:33,160
Mother!

693
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,400
But...

694
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,190
But in this world,

695
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,720
where can I go

696
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:48,720
except Earl Dongping's Mansion?

697
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:51,000
You still have me, Mother.

698
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:55,150
From now on, I'll support you.

699
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:56,600
We don't need others.

700
00:31:57,590 --> 00:31:59,040
We'll have our own home.

701
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,590
But Si...

702
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,840
Don't worry.

703
00:32:08,480 --> 00:32:09,550
She told me to come here

704
00:32:09,550 --> 00:32:10,470
to get you out.

705
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,320
I see.

706
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:19,350
Rumors are spreading in the Palace

707
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,960
that you're seductive.

708
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,430
Who knows

709
00:32:22,790 --> 00:32:24,430
you're still a virgin?

710
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,910
Neither did I know

711
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:29,190
you'd be fooled by rumors, Your Highness.

712
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,560
Some attitude you got.

713
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,480
You're still unruly.

714
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,190
You've scolded me

715
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:38,600
and had me checked.

716
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:41,280
May I go home now?

717
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,750
This is my hall,

718
00:32:42,750 --> 00:32:43,720
not somewhere

719
00:32:44,070 --> 00:32:47,320
you can come and go as you please.

720
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:48,990
Servant,

721
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:50,570
fetch Important Principles for Girls.

722
00:32:51,510 --> 00:32:53,590
Have her copy the book until she's obedient.

723
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:08,430
Has anyone in this house

724
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:11,560
ever respected me at all?

725
00:33:11,720 --> 00:33:12,800
Who am I?

726
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:15,000
Do I have a name?

727
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:18,910
I'm merely your pawn!

728
00:33:20,510 --> 00:33:22,510
I had to compete.

729
00:33:22,510 --> 00:33:24,480
I had to fight

730
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,920
in order to

731
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:28,240
keep a foothold in this house!

732
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:34,960
But I never meant to kill anyone.

733
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:39,720
I was also tricked by others.

734
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:44,040
("Time passes like running water.)

735
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:46,040
(Life is as short as morning dew.")

736
00:33:46,590 --> 00:33:47,670
(Who knows)

737
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,630
(my sworn enemy)

738
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,190
(saved my life)

739
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:54,520
(and gave us a way out?)

740
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:55,710
(Mother,)

741
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:58,240
(we'll forever remember her kindness.)

742
00:33:59,310 --> 00:34:00,200
(If Si needs)

743
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:01,760
(our help in the future,)

744
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:03,630
(we'll come back at once.)

745
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:10,630
Miss Si.

746
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,360
Since you arrived,

747
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:16,310
you've had to kneel and copy the book.

748
00:34:16,710 --> 00:34:17,840
I feel sorry for you.

749
00:34:18,510 --> 00:34:20,520
Serve Miss Si tea.

750
00:34:23,110 --> 00:34:24,030
Thanks, Princess Qi.

751
00:34:24,710 --> 00:34:26,080
You've never copied this before.

752
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,960
It takes time to learn.

753
00:34:28,480 --> 00:34:29,830
The first step is always difficult.

754
00:34:29,830 --> 00:34:31,150
I'll teach you.

755
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,280
No, thanks.

756
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:43,150
I went through the same steps the first time

757
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,630
I paid my respects to her.

758
00:34:45,110 --> 00:34:46,190
When I was a girl,

759
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,710
I was also spoiled by my parents.

760
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:50,920
They always indulged me

761
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:51,840
and pampered me.

762
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,630
I had never suffered such humiliation.

763
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:56,110
I cried for three days when I got back.

764
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,710
Now, I can only hope to be

765
00:34:59,710 --> 00:35:00,920
a mother-in-law someday.

766
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,320
Miss Si,

767
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,400
you did much better than me just now.

768
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,360
If we have each other's backs,

769
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:09,110
it's better than suffering alone.

770
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:13,310
You probably don't know, Princess Qi.

771
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:15,560
My mother passed away a long time ago.

772
00:35:15,880 --> 00:35:16,920
It was my aunt

773
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:18,790
who was in charge of our house.

774
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,560
My aunt was

775
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:22,040
quite pretentious.

776
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:23,920
She was stingy

777
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,230
but had to look generous.

778
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:29,030
When she finally gave us a bolt of cloth

779
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:30,030
and some coal,

780
00:35:30,030 --> 00:35:31,480
she'd go on and on about it

781
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:33,360
so that everyone in town

782
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,280
would know.

783
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:37,750
What are you implying?

784
00:35:38,070 --> 00:35:39,690
Are you blaming me for not helping you...?

785
00:35:39,690 --> 00:35:40,830
I'd appreciate it if you did,

786
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,840
but that wasn't your duty.

787
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,440
Thank you

788
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,400
for your tea,

789
00:35:45,630 --> 00:35:46,790
and thank you

790
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:48,510
for putting in a good word for me

791
00:35:48,510 --> 00:35:49,430
with Consort Xian.

792
00:35:49,710 --> 00:35:51,440
But after all these years

793
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:53,190
of dealing with

794
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:55,230
my two-faced aunt at home,

795
00:35:55,630 --> 00:35:57,230
I can tell

796
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,230
good and bad intentions.

797
00:35:59,670 --> 00:36:02,000
Consort Xian insulted me openly

798
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,240
while you

799
00:36:03,550 --> 00:36:05,080
didn't actually respect me either.

800
00:36:05,630 --> 00:36:06,920
You invited me to your banquet

801
00:36:07,030 --> 00:36:08,750
but had me sit at the end of the table.

802
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,270
You spoke for me

803
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:12,190
only to put on a show.

804
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:13,440
Such

805
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:15,270
little kindness as a handout

806
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:17,670
isn't any better than the cloth

807
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,720
and coal

808
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:20,270
from my aunt.

809
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,960
If you expected to win me over

810
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,840
with such petty favors,

811
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:27,360
that'd be absurd.

812
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:32,080
You mistake it, Miss Si.

813
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,840
You just said it yourself.

814
00:36:34,110 --> 00:36:35,400
Now that there are two of us,

815
00:36:35,670 --> 00:36:36,840
you won't

816
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,310
suffer alone.

817
00:36:38,590 --> 00:36:39,920
Is everything happening

818
00:36:40,030 --> 00:36:41,400
as you expected?

819
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:43,920
I didn't know Mother

820
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:45,480
- would be so mad...
- Say no more.

821
00:36:46,070 --> 00:36:48,000
From now on, if you don't set me up,

822
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,520
I won't mess with you.

823
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:50,920
You may leave.

824
00:36:54,510 --> 00:36:55,600
Good luck with the copying.

825
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:04,840
Did Jiang Si really say so?

826
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:06,880
Yes.

827
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:09,110
I was right outside the room.

828
00:37:09,590 --> 00:37:10,630
I heard it loud and clear.

829
00:37:11,550 --> 00:37:12,400
Who gave her

830
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:13,750
such a ready tongue?

831
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:17,080
She barely knows Zhang's wife.

832
00:37:18,670 --> 00:37:19,630
Unexpectedly,

833
00:37:19,630 --> 00:37:21,590
she said all that I had meant to

834
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:23,550
get off my chest

835
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:24,750
all these years.

836
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:28,080
Zhang's wife is such a hypocrite.

837
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:31,840
Back then, she stood right there,

838
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:34,440
keeping her head down when I lectured her.

839
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:37,670
I thought she was a doormat.

840
00:37:38,280 --> 00:37:39,360
But once she got home,

841
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,190
she had the Grand Preceptor

842
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:43,000
complain to His Majesty about me,

843
00:37:43,110 --> 00:37:44,560
making me look like

844
00:37:44,710 --> 00:37:46,520
a mean mother-in-law.

845
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,630
Alight then. She called me mean.

846
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:52,670
I shall act accordingly.

847
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:00,920
Princess Qi.

848
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,000
Prince Yan,

849
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:06,710
are you here to see Miss Si?

850
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,440
She has

851
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:12,110
suffered a lot.

852
00:38:12,230 --> 00:38:13,150
What happened?

853
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:15,400
As obedient as Princess Qi seems,

854
00:38:16,030 --> 00:38:17,360
she's deep and scheming.

855
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,790
I see

856
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:22,190
that although Miss Si is unruly,

857
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,400
she's candid and honest,

858
00:38:24,670 --> 00:38:25,920
not the trouble-making sort.

859
00:38:26,590 --> 00:38:28,520
You've kept her for too long.

860
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,920
I wonder if Prince Yan

861
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:32,150
will come to look for her.

862
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,230
Shall I

863
00:38:34,230 --> 00:38:35,400
send her back now?

864
00:38:36,670 --> 00:38:38,520
Do you think I'm afraid of my son?

865
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,560
You aren't, of course.

866
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:45,110
Sticks always work better than carrots.

867
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,960
I'm their mother-in-law.

868
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:48,070
Whether the two of them

869
00:38:48,070 --> 00:38:49,480
are pretentious or stubborn,

870
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:51,630
they'll have to obey me.

871
00:38:52,110 --> 00:38:53,030
Keep grinding her down.

872
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:55,080
Your Highness, Prince Yan came.

873
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,520
He came so soon.

874
00:38:56,710 --> 00:38:57,960
Have him wait outside.

875
00:39:03,480 --> 00:39:05,670
Consort Xian, where's Jiang Si?

876
00:39:23,150 --> 00:39:24,920
